      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARRY ETHICS (2) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, rewarded with a win last time at Gosford over 388m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Looks to have an edge on most of these. SWIFT WIND (7) was out of the placings latest but three back was a Maiden winner in quick time (29.74) at The Gardens in a Maiden. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Expected to do much better this time. ANCESTRAL QUEEN (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (30.15) at this track behind Release Point in a Grade 5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Expected to feature. BANDIT BLAZE (6) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
